00:00:06.240 --> 00:00:12.240
 Welcome to the teaching videos of the Lattissima Touch Cup setting. 

00:00:12.240 --> 00:00:15.840
 This machine has 6 buttons: 

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:22.920
 Extremely espresso, espresso, mug of coffee, latte macchiato, cappuccino and fresh hot milk foam. 

00:00:23.200 --> 00:00:27.520
 Coffee or milk coffee will automatically stop flowing when it reaches the original set cup size. 

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:31.840
 You can set the cup size yourself as you like. 

00:00:35.160 --> 00:00:40.000
 After booting up, about 25 seconds to warm up. Place the cup under the coffee spout. 

00:00:41.520 --> 00:00:50.720
 Put the capsule on the top cover. Close the top cover. 

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:56.320
 Long press the button for three seconds, 

00:00:56.680 --> 00:01:02.480
 The button light will flash quickly and enter the preset mode. 

00:01:03.160 --> 00:01:07.400
 Press and hold the button during coffee brewing. 

00:01:08.360 --> 00:01:12.000
 Release the button until the desired amount of cup is reached. 

00:01:12.760 --> 00:01:16.880
 The button light will flash 3 times to confirm the new cup volume. 

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:23.920
 From now on, press this button and the coffee will stay until the new cup has been set. 

00:01:30.680 --> 00:01:32.560
 Set the amount of cappuccino cup 

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:38.280
 Slide the vapor port connection to the right to connect the quick cappuccino system to the coffee machine. 

00:01:38.680 --> 00:01:40.960
 Warm up time is about 15 seconds. 

00:01:41.640 --> 00:01:48.160
 Place the cappuccino cup under the coffee spout and adjust the milk nozzle to the appropriate position. 

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:55.400
 Rotate the milk shake adjustment knob (turn to the right or left) to adjust the amount of milk foam. 

00:01:55.840 --> 00:02:03.640
 We recommend rotating the cappuccino to the minimum amount of milk foam; the maximum amount of milk is used to modulate the latte macchiato. 

00:02:04.440 --> 00:02:08.720
 Press and hold the cappuccino cup button for three seconds, the button light will flash quickly into the preset mode. 

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:15.560
 The warm milk foam will begin to be modulated. 

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:20.960
 Press and hold the button during milk bubble modulation, 

00:02:21.800 --> 00:02:24.800
 Release the button until the desired amount of cup is reached. 

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:28.920
 Long press the same button to start brewing coffee, 

00:02:29.240 --> 00:02:32.520
 Release the button until the desired water level is reached. 

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:36.880
 The button light will flash 3 times to confirm the new cup volume. 

00:02:37.400 --> 00:02:40.320
 From now on, press the cappuccino button, 

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:45.280
 The amount of coffee and milk will stay until the new cup has been set. 

